PLAYER STATS HELP
INTELLIGENCE
Intelligence(INT): The intelligence stat is an indicator of your character's ability to remember things and perform feats of logical reasoning. It plays an important role in casting arcane magic and in determining your mana capacity. Eventually, intelligence will be used when memorizing blueprints and in conducting research.

See also: ~CREFstats, strength, dexterity, constitution, speed, willpower, empathy, charisma
